{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回「魔眼」：唐麟在帐篷中被一剑穿心而死，凶器是名剑\"魔眼\"。众人在尸体旁发现十三枚蜀中唐门的花芒铁器暗器，一名捡起暗器的人当场中毒身亡。驼子拔出魔眼剑，指出这是天下最锋利的七柄剑之一，并追问剑的来历。小方承认自己就是方伟，魔眼剑的持有者。他冷静自辩：若真是他杀了唐麟，绝不会将如此珍贵的名剑留在现场。驼子认可其推理，帮他暂时化解众人杀气。驼子断定凶手并非队伍中人，但要求小方留在队中不得离开。小方内心怀疑卫天鹏、水银、无名剑客甚至卜鹰，但在沙漠空旷环境下无人能潜入帐篷行凶。入夜后，藏族战士加答将自己最珍贵的喀巴沙靴子献给小方，恳求他尽快离开——因为班察巴那即将归来。波娃听到\"班察巴那\"四字后惊恐万分，告诉小方此人就是圣母峰下第一位勇士\"五花箭神\"，催促他快逃。全章以班察巴那即将到来的巨大威胁收尾，悬念陡升。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能碰，碰不得。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知角色",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是魔眼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "魔眼！什么是魔眼？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这柄剑的名字就叫做魔眼，是当今天下最锋利的七柄剑之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐麟虽然是蜀中唐门的旁支子弟，却是唐家可以数得出的几位高手之一，他的出手不但快而准，而且还练过峨眉的仙猿剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我想你一定也听说过这柄剑的来历。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这柄剑是不是已经落入一个姓方的年轻剑客手里。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这个姓方的人是不是叫方伟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你就是方伟？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这柄剑是我的，我的出手一向不慢，要杀唐麟也不难。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过这次要真是我杀了唐麟，我为什么要将这柄剑留下来？难道我是个疯子？难道我生怕别人不知道是我杀了他？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这柄剑我得来并不容易，我绝不会把它留给别人的，不管那个人是死是活都一样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果你们有这样一把剑，你们杀人后会不会把它留下来？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是凶手也绝不会是我们这队伍中的人，这里没有人能一次杀死唐麟，也没有人能从你手中夺去这柄剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我已经有两三天没有看到这柄剑了，你应该记得，你第一次见到我的时候，这柄剑并不在我手里。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "怎么会不在你手里？在谁的手里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在凶手还没有查出来之前，你还是不能离开，这柄剑你也不能带走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_tuo_zi",
      "text": "在凶手还没有查出来之前，就算有人赶我走，我也不会走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明天我们不走，谁也不能离开队伍，三十五岁以下的男人，不管有没有练过武，都要加入警卫。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好班察巴那明天一定会回来了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这是喀巴沙。我只有这一双喀巴沙，就好像你只有一把魔眼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我没有穿过这双喀巴沙，我的脚有臭汗，我不配穿，可是我本来也绝不会把它留给别人，可是我现在献给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "text": "为什么？我不会把魔眼献给你，你为什么要把这双喀巴沙献给我。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你要走了，要走很远很远的路，要走得很快很快，你需要一双好靴子保护你的脚。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "text": "我为什么要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为班察巴那就要回来了。别人怀疑你，可是别人不敢动你，别人都怕你，怕你怕得要命。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是班察巴那不怕，班察巴那谁都不怕，班察巴那一回来，你就会像马沙一样死掉。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "text": "班察巴那，他……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你刚才说了四个字，你在说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "text": "班察巴那。我正想问我的朋友，班察巴那是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "班察巴那要来了，你一定要快走、快走。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bo_wa",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知道不知道圣母峰下第一位勇士是谁？你有没有听说过五花箭神？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_wa",
      "speaker_name": "波娃",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "班察巴那就是五花箭神。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    }
  ],
